<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <%- include("partials/head.ejs") %>
        <title>High Street Gym - Home</title>
    </head>
    <body>
      <% const accessRole = null %>
      <% const firstName = null %>
        <%- include("partials/header.ejs", {accessRole, firstName}) %>  
        <main>
               
            <section class="hero-section">
                <div class="hero-content">
                  <h1>Welcome to High Street Gym</h1>
                  <p>Your ultimate destination for fitness and wellness</p>
                  <div class="cta-button"><a href="/signup">Join Now</a></div>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-image">
                  <img src="img/hero-image.jpg" alt="hero image" />
                </div>
              </section>
              <section class="aboutus-section">
                <h2>About Us</h2>
              <p>Welcome to our gym! We are committed to helping you achieve your fitness goals and lead a healthier lifestyle. Our team of experienced trainers and staff are here to support you every step of the way.</p>
                <p>At our gym, we offer a wide range of fitness classes, state-of-the-art equipment, and personalized training programs to cater to individuals of all fitness levels. Whether you're a beginner or a seasoned athlete, there's something for everyone here.</p>
                <p>We believe that fitness should be fun and enjoyable, which is why we strive to create a welcoming and inclusive environment for all our members. Join us today and start your fitness journey with us!</p>
                <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                <p>Our mission is to empower individuals to live healthier, happier lives through fitness and wellness. We are dedicated to providing high-quality fitness programs, personalized training, and ongoing support to help our members reach their fitness goals and achieve long-term success.</p>
                <h3>Our Team</h3>
                <p>Our team consists of certified fitness trainers, nutritionists, and wellness experts who are passionate about helping others achieve their fitness goals. We are committed to providing our members with the knowledge, guidance, and motivation they need to succeed.</p>
                <h3>Contact Us</h3>
                <p>If you have any questions or would like to learn more about our gym, feel free to <a href="/locations">contact us.</a> We'd love to hear from you!</p>
              </section>

              <section class="Locations-section">
                <h2>Locations</h2>
                We have locations in five suburbs.
              </section>
            
        </main>
        <%- include("partials/footer.ejs") %>
    </body>
</html>
